  "detailed_description": "Sarah is having a nightmare. Only you can wake her up. To achieve this you will have to find your way through the maze.<br><br>When playing this game, you agree to finish it before asking for a refund, unless you are a coward.<br><br>Keep an eye on the clock, time passes by fast.<br><br>After two hours the achievement will be locked forever.<br><br>For that you will have to try many paths, again and again.<br><br><strong>The game contains more than 100 different paths, but only one to salvation.</strong><br><br><br><strong>Throw flares to remember your tracks.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.mp4?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br><strong>Beware of environmental destruction features.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/9d7b9eed9441d24e7a7cd26efdff2248.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/9d7b9eed9441d24e7a7cd26efdff2248.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Pay attention to noises and take in consideration writings.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/26ac00cfd8c0edb2ef7db7336bad89e0.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/26ac00cfd8c0edb2ef7db7336bad89e0.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/26ac00cfd8c0edb2ef7db7336bad89e0.mp4?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Push through obstacles.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/3330d37fd4231feabf4eeb055d1cfad8.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/3330d37fd4231feabf4eeb055d1cfad8.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/3330d37fd4231feabf4eeb055d1cfad8.mp4?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Don't get caught by the monster.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/b1a4651601ecd14cd811391372073c13.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/b1a4651601ecd14cd811391372073c13.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/b1a4651601ecd14cd811391372073c13.mp4?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>One last tip, <strong>NEVER STAY MORE THEN 45 SECONDS IN THE SAME POSITION !</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "Sarah is having a nightmare. Only you can wake her up. To achieve this you will have to find your way through the maze.<br><br>When playing this game, you agree to finish it before asking for a refund, unless you are a coward.<br><br>Keep an eye on the clock, time passes by fast.<br><br>After two hours the achievement will be locked forever.<br><br>For that you will have to try many paths, again and again.<br><br><strong>The game contains more than 100 different paths, but only one to salvation.</strong><br><br><br><strong>Throw flares to remember your tracks.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/e0eeab143fd9bfa74a9ee27a6ec6b675.mp4?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br><strong>Beware of environmental destruction features.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/9d7b9eed9441d24e7a7cd26efdff2248.poster.avif?t=1683652955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011860/extras/9d7b9eed9441d24e7a7cd26efdff2248.webm?t=1683652955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Pay attention to noises and take in consideration writings.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store